  "subject": "Publish properties for Portal/SDK versions",
  "commit_message": "Publish properties for Portal/SDK versions\n\nThe portal release candidate is on branch release-1.3.0.\nThe same branch is cloned for portal/sdk, instead of the desired release-1.3.1.\nProvide suitable property files for SDK versions 1.3.0 and 1.3.1.\n\nIssue: PORTAL-134\nChange-Id: Ie6e55ac0dc57f2caa6f4de954bd3f690c4332d26\nSigned-off-by: Christopher Lott (cl778h) <clott@research.att.com>\n",
